PrecisOrder which provides for (a) the withdrawal of the entrustment conferred upon the Canadian National Railway Company with respect to a railway right- of-way located in the City of THUNDER BAY, Ontario, extending a total distance of 2.27 miles from Memorial Avenue to an ore dock on the shores of Lake Superior, for a total area of some 67.78 acres, including the property comprising Hill Yard and the ore dock, and (b) the sale of the property so withdrawn to the Canadian National Railway Company.
